Ow! Oh, the ground.

25
00:04:05,162 --> 00:04:07,204
Oh... Oh...

26
00:04:07,289 --> 00:04:09,832
Oh, I made it.

27
00:04:09,958 --> 00:04:13,002
I made it! There is a God.

28
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:15,671
Hallelujaaaaaa!

29
